Package: @PKG_DEB_NAME@
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Likewise-CIFS Server
 The Likewise-CIFS Server is a fully featured SMBv1 and SMBv2
 SMB/CIFS file server for Microsoft, Linux, Unix, and OS X clients.
 Includes the Netlogon domain controller location service (netlogond),
 Likewise Security Authority (lsassd), Likewise I/O Manager (lwiod),
 Likewise Service Manager (lwsmd), Likewise Registry (lwregd), and
 the necessary DCE/RPC runtime and network services.  For more details,
 please visit http://www.likewiseopen.org/

